lead_paragraph: Kelsey Mitchell hit five 3-pointers and scored 23 points and had six assists to lead No. 14 Ohio State to an 87-62 win over Minnesota in the Big Ten opener on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: No. 14 Ohio State Opens Big 10 With 87-62 Win Over Minnesota
